``to html``
, added initial work on 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2297] winget support
, fixed some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2321] soft link-related issues
, removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2347] some unnecessary bat features we weren't using
avranju added the ability to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2314] disable the welcome banner
Amanita-muscaria made the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2320] history file location configurable
jonathandturner released 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2325] version 0.18
, moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2345] starship external
, made a new 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2348] default/extra set of features and plugins
.
samhedin fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2326] exit scripts when working with per-directory environments
JosephTLyons updated the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2332] random dice example
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2334] removed 
``--with-symlink-targets``
 from 
``ls``
andrasio added listing the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2333] features Nu was built with as part of 
``version``
, updated 
``update``
 and 
``insert``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2339] fully drain their optional blocks
, 
``histogram``
 now can use an 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2341] additional column for the histogram value
, added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2340] percent column to 
``histogram``
coolshaurya added the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2336] commit hash to 
``version``
jzaefferer added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/demo/pull/57] tracking client-side errors in the demo with the Sentry
